title: Great Doctor Miss Nine
overview: The animation tells the story of the modern, glamorous, genius doctor Jun Jiu who accidentally fell to her death in an elixir auction and ends up in the body of Miss Jiu from the past. Miss Jiu was originally the direct daughter of the Jun family, one of the two great families in the imperial city. Because of the death of both parents, the family sent her to the Jun family in Fengluo City. Jun Jiu inherited all the memories of Miss Jiu and vowed revenge. In this world of immortal cultivation, she first cleansed her muscles and marrow through her amazing medical skills to improve her cultivation talent, and then made good friends and paved the way carefully. Watch how Jun Jiu kills her enemies, cleanses the Feng Luo family, and begins her legendary story of a generation of heavenly daughters.
